data.description: Seller is ready to move and has the C.O. certification in hand. This lovely 4-5 bedroom home located in the desirable Crossroads development boasts many upgrades. Foyer, formal living room have crown molding.  Living & dining rooms have hardwood floors with dining room having oak mains coating and decorative trim.  The large kitchen with many cabinets includes a wine fridge and double convection oven and separate breakfast area with waterproof wood laminate floors.  The family room with fireplace opens to a large covered porch leading to the pool. Half of the basement is finished and the other ideal for storage or workouts. In the master bedroom you'll find his and her closets and a new bathroom with porcelain tile.  The unfinished 5th bedroom would be great for a home office or plenty of storage.  Overall it is a great home in a great community that you can make your forever home 2018-10-19
